        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "Every gemstone and pearl in a Kinsoul Energy bracelet is 100% natural — never synthetic, never lab-created, never coated. We source freshwater pearls from farms in China's Zhejiang province and gemstones from regions including Brazil, Afghanistan, South Africa, India, and Madagascar. Each order includes a certificate of authenticity."
